<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="js" lang="en">

<head>

	<title>Subsidy authoriation request | MyService</title>
	<% include ../../../../partials/head.ejs %>
</head>

<body class="uikit-body uikit-grid uikit-refactor">
	<noscript>
		<p role="alert">This website needs JavaScript to work properly.</p>
	</noscript>
	<nav class="uikit-skip-link">
		<a class="uikit-skip-link__link" href="#main-content">Skip to main content</a>
	</nav>
	<% include ../../../../partials/header-topbar.ejs %>
	<% include ../../../../partials/header-nom-rep.ejs %>

	<main id="main-content">
    <div class="section-feature border-bottom--mild margin-above--none margin-below--none padding-below">
      <div class="container margin-above--none">
        <h1 class="margin-above--none ss-align--center">
          <span class="heading">Posting order</span>
        </h1>
      </div>
    </div>
		<div class="container">
			<div id="progressbar">
				<div id="percentage">
					<p id="percentage_value"></p>
				</div>

			</div>

			<div class="form-group">
				<label class="uikit-text-input__label" for="toggle-buttons">Do you currently hold a posting order which will prevent you from meeting the 12 month occupancy requirement?</label>
				<div id="posting" class="radio-toggle">
					<label class="on label-left" for="posting-yes">
						<input id="posting-yes" type="radio" name="toggle-buttons">
						<span>Yes</span>
					</label>
					<label class="off label-right" for="posting-no">
						<input id="posting-no" type="radio" name="toggle-buttons">
						<span>No</span>
					</label>
				</div>
			</div>


			<div id="posting-yes-div" style="display: none;">
				<div class="form-group">
					<label class="uikit-text-input__label" for="textArea">Please provide details</label>
					<textarea id="textArea" name="textArea" rows="5"></textarea>
				</div>
				<div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--error" role="alert">
					<p>I understand that subsidy may cease if I stop occupying the property within 12 months following the commencement of subsidy payments or the completion of building work.</p>
					<p>If I am unable to occupy the home for the 12 month occupancy period, I understand that I must be approved for a shorter period of occupancy to be eligible for continued subsidy payments.</p><p>I also understand that I must apply for a reduced occupancy period within a reasoanble period of time of vacating the DHOAS subsidised property.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<h1>
				<span class="heading">Lump sum</span>
			</h1>

			<div class="form-group">
				<label class="uikit-text-input__label" for="toggle-buttons-0">Have you requested the lump sum on your current Subsidy Certificate?</label>
				<div class="uikit-page-alerts" role="alert">
					<p>If you select 'Yes' you must be able to agree to both statement 1 and 2 to be eligible for the lump sum (unless you are applying as a surviving partner). If you cannot confirm 'Yes' to both of the statements, you are not eligible for the lump sum.</p>
					          <p>You can find out more about DHOAS lump sum payments on the
            <a href="http://dhoas.gov.au/8.-lump-sum.html" rel="external" target="_blank">DHOAS website</a></p>
				</div>
				<div id="lump-sum-previous" class="radio-toggle">
					<label class="on label-left" for="lump-sum-previous-yes">
						<input id="lump-sum-previous-yes" type="radio" name="toggle-buttons-0">
						<span>Yes</span>
					</label>
					<label class="off label-right" for="lump-sum-previous-no">
						<input id="lump-sum-previous-no" type="radio" name="toggle-buttons-0">
						<span>No</span>
					</label>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="form-group" id="lump-sum-previous-no-div" style="display: none;">
				<label class="uikit-text-input__label" for="toggle-buttons">Do you want to make an application for a lump sum now?</label>
				<div id="lump-sum-now" class="radio-toggle">
					<label class="on label-left" for="lump-sum-now-yes">
						<input id="lump-sum-now-yes" type="radio" name="toggle-buttons">
						<span>Yes</span>
					</label>
					<label class="off label-right" for="lump-sum-now-no">
						<input id="lump-sum-now-no" type="radio" name="toggle-buttons">
						<span>No</span>
					</label>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div id="lump-sum-previous-yes-div" style="display: none;">
				<div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--error" role="alert">
					<p>I confirm the declarations made on my application for Subsidy Certificate form are correct in that:</p>
					<ol>
						<li>I expect that I will continue to provide service in the Australian Defence Force (ADF), where the service is considered effective for DHOAS purposes, for a period of at least 12 months after the payment of subsidy is authorised. *I acknowledge that the Scheme Administrator or the Department of Defence may recover an amount equal to the lump sum subsidy paid to me if I cease to be a member of the ADF within 12 month after the payment subsidy is authorised. (*The declaration does not apply if you are applying for a lump sum as a surviving partner); and</li>
						<li>Whilst I have been a member of the ADF, I have not previously purchased a home, other than the one that is the subject of this application for Subsidy Certificate, and this property was purchased after I received my Subsidy Certificate.</li>
						<p><strong>NOTE: </strong>If you have less than 12 months of entitlement remaining after you receive the lump sum payment, and subsequently transfer to the Reserves, your monthly DHOAS payments may cease.</p>
					</ol>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div id="lump-sum-now-no-div" style="display: none;">
				
			</div>			
			<div id="lump-sum-now-yes-div" style="display: none;">
				<!-- -->
      <div id="lumpSum-eligibility">

        <h4>Check your eligibility for a lump sum payment</h4>
        <!-- Land ownership -->

        <div class="form-group simple-box">
          <!-- Eligibility question 1 -->

          <fieldset id="landOwnership">
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-8 margin-above">
              <legend class="legend-label legend-label--light">While serving in the ADF have you, or you and your partner, previously owned a 50% or greater stake in a home, either
                to live in or for an investment?
              </legend>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 margin-above">
              <div class="mys-radio-group mys-radio-group--cols-2">
                <label class="mys-radio">
                  <input id="landOwnership-no" class="mys-radio__control" type="radio" name="landOwnership" value="landOwnership-no">
                  <span class="mys-radio__box">Yes</span>
                </label>
                <label class="mys-radio">
                  <input id="landOwnership-yes" class="mys-radio__control" type="radio" name="landOwnership" value="landOwnership-yes">
                  <span class="mys-radio__box">No</span>
                </label>
              </div>
            </div>
          </fieldset>

          <!-- Eligibility question 2 -->
          <fieldset id="continueService">
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-8">
              <legend class="legend-label legend-label--light">Do you expect to leave the ADF within 12 months of your subsidy payment being authorised?</legend>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
              <div class="mys-radio-group mys-radio-group--cols-2">
                <label class="mys-radio">
                  <input id="continueService-no" class="mys-radio__control" type="radio" name="continueService" value="continueService-no">
                  <span class="mys-radio__box">Yes</span>
                </label>
                <label class="mys-radio">
                  <input id="continueService-yes" class="mys-radio__control" type="radio" name="continueService" value="continueService-yes">
                  <span class="mys-radio__box">No</span>
                </label>
              </div>
            </div>
          </fieldset>
        </div>

<!-- 
    WORDING FOR ID "eligable__yes" 
    TO BE ADVISED BY DHOAS/SIMON
-->
        <div id="eligible__yes" class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--success margin-below--none" style="display:none;">You are eligible to request a lump sum payment.</div>
<!-- 
    WORDING FOR ID "eligable__no" 
    TO BE ADVISED BY DHOAS/SIMON
-->
        <div id="eligible__no" class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--warning margin-below--extra" style="display:none;">You are not eligible to request a lump sum payment.
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Lump sum amount -->

      <div id="lumpSum-amount" class="form-group" style="display:none;">

        <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--info margin-above--none margin-below--extra">
          <h4>Important things to know</h4>

          <p>The maximum lump sum amount cannot exceed 48 months of payments.</p>
          <p>Your monthly DHOAS payments may cease if you transfer to the Reserves and have less than 12 months of entitlement remaining after your lump sum payment is received.
          </p>

        </div>



        <div class="form-group" id="purpose">
          <label class="uikit-text-input__label" for="radio-buttons">How much of your entitlement do you want to receive as a lump sum?
            <span class="hint display-block">You can choose how many months of your entitlement you would like to convert into a single lump sum payment.</span>
          </label>
          <p class="uiToolKitCheckBox">
            <label class="uikit-control-input" id="op2">
              <input class="uikit-control-input__input" type="radio" id="maximum" name="months">
              <span class="uikit-control-input__text">request the maximum amount</span>
            </label>
          </p>
          <p class="uiToolKitCheckBox">
            <label class="uikit-control-input" id="op1">
              <input class="uikit-control-input__input" type="radio" id="monthlychoice" name="months">
              <span class="uikit-control-input__text">request a specific number of months</span>
            </label>
          </p>

          <div id="monthlyamount">
            <fieldset class="form-group form-group--secondary">
              <span class="input-support-text">
                <span class="hint">I would like to convert&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>
              </span>
              <input class="uikit-text-input input-small mm" name="InterestInProperty" id="monthlyfigure" type="number">
              <span class="input-support-text">&nbsp;
                <span class="hint">months into a lump sum payment.</span>
              </span>
            </fieldset>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- <div class="display-inline-block margin-below">
                <input class="uikit-text-input input-small yyyy" name="months" id="months" type="number"> months, or &nbsp;&nbsp;</div>
              <div class="display-inline-block uiToolKitCheckBox">
                <label class="uikit-control-input">
                  <input class="uikit-control-input__input" type="checkbox" id="checkbox1" name="checkbox">
                  <span class="uikit-control-input__text">Maximum amount</span>
                </label>
              </div> -->

        <p class="margin-above--large">
          <span class="heading heading--spacer"></span>
        </p>

        <div class="margin-below--large">
          <h4>You must agree with the following before your lump sum payment request can be submitted</h4>
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-8">
                <label class="uikit-control-input">
                  <input id="agreementOne" class="uikit-control-input__input agreement" type="checkbox" name="agreement">
<!-- 
    WORDING FOR BELOW SPAN STARTING 
    WITH "I acknowledge" TO BE
    ADVISED BY DHOAS/SIMON
-->
                  <span class="uikit-control-input__text">I acknowledge that the Scheme Administrator or the Department of Defence may recover an amount equal to my lump sum
                    subsidy
                    payment if I cease to be a member of the ADF within 12 months after payment is authorised.
                  </span>
                </label>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>


				<!-- -->
			</div>
			<div class="pagination margin-above--extra">
				<button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary " onclick="window.location.href='/auth/claim/dhoas/sar3' ">Previous</button>
				<button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary" onclick="window.location.href = '#open-modal'">Cancel application</button>
				<div class="floated">
					<button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary" onclick="window.location.href = '/auth/claim'">Save and exit</button>
					<button class="uikit-btn btnNext" id="btnNext" onclick="window.location.href = '/auth/claim/dhoas/sar5'">Save and next</button>
				</div>
			</div>

			<% include ../../../../partials/claims-cancel-modal.ejs %>
		</div>

	</main>

	<% include ../../../../partials/footer.ejs %>

</body>

<script type="text/javascript">

	$("#posting").on("change", "input[type='radio']", function () {
		if($("#posting-yes").prop("checked")) {
			$("#posting-yes-div").css("display", "block");
			$("#posting-yes-no").css("display", "none");
		} else {
			$("#posting-yes-div").css("display", "none");
			$("#posting-yes-no").css("display", "block");
		}
	});

	$("#lump-sum-previous").on("change", "input[type='radio']", function () {
		if($("#lump-sum-previous-yes").prop("checked")) {
			$("#lump-sum-previous-yes-div").css("display", "block");
			$("#lump-sum-previous-no-div").css("display", "none");
		} else {
			$("#lump-sum-previous-yes-div").css("display", "none");
			$("#lump-sum-previous-no-div").css("display", "block");
		}
	});
	$("#lump-sum-now").on("change", "input[type='radio']", function () {
		if($("#lump-sum-now-yes").prop("checked")) {
			$("#lump-sum-now-yes-div").css("display", "block");
			$("#lump-sum-now-no-div").css("display", "none");
		} else {
			$("#lump-sum-now-yes-div").css("display", "none");
			$("#lump-sum-now-no-div").css("display", "block");
		}
	});



    $('#landOwnership').click(function () {
      if (radiosChecked()) {
        if (showEligibility()) {
          $("#eligible__yes").show();
          $("#lumpSum-amount").show();
          $("#eligible__no").hide();
        } else {
          $("#eligible__no").show();
          $("#lumpSum-amount").hide();
          $("#eligible__yes").hide();
        }
      }
    });
    $('#continueService').click(function () {
      if (radiosChecked()) {
        if (showEligibility()) {
          $("#eligible__yes").show();
          $("#lumpSum-amount").show();
          $("#eligible__no").hide();
        } else {
          $("#eligible__no").show();
          $("#lumpSum-amount").hide();
          $("#eligible__yes").hide();
        }
      }
    });

    $('#continueService-yes').click(function () {
      continueValue = true
    });
    $('#continueService-no').click(function () {
      continueValue = false
    });
    $('#landOwnership-yes').click(function () {
      landValue = true
    });
    $('#landOwnership-no').click(function () {
      landValue = false
    });




    function radiosChecked() {
      var landChecked = false;
      $('#landOwnership').find('input').each(function () {
        if (this.checked) {
          landChecked = true;
        }
      })
      var continueChecked = false;
      $('#continueService').find('input').each(function () {
        if (this.checked) {
          continueChecked = true
        }
      })
      if (landChecked && continueChecked) {
        return true
      } else {
        return false
      }
    }

    function showEligibility() {
      if (this.landValue && this.continueValue) {
        return true;
      } else {
        return false;
      }
    }


    var buttonon = true;

    $("#next").click(function () {

      if ($("#reservist")[0].checked) {
        $(".off > input").each(function () {
          if (!$(this)[0].checked) {
            buttonon = false;
          }
        })
        if (buttonon) {
          window.location.href = "/auth/claim/health-card-blocker";
          return
        }
      }
      window.location.href = "/auth/claim/health-card1";
    });

    $("#monthlyamount").hide();
    $("#monthlychoice").click(function () {
      // debugger
      if ($(this).prop('checked')) {
        $("#monthlyamount").show();
      } else {
        $("#monthlyamount").hide();
      }
    });
    $("#maximum").click(function () {
      // debugger
      if ($(this).prop('checked')) {
        $("#monthlyamount").hide();
      }
    });
</script>

</html>
